  "content": {
    "en": "<div data-test-render-count=\"1\"><div class=\"group\" style=\"height: auto; opacity: 1; transform: none;\"><div class=\"contents\"><div data-is-streaming=\"false\" class=\"group relative relative pb-3\" style=\"opacity: 1; transform: none;\"><div class=\"font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8\"><div class=\"standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown\"><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\"></p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"h-px w-full pointer-events-none\"></div><p></p><div data-test-render-count=\"1\"><div class=\"group\" style=\"height: auto; opacity: 1; transform: none;\"><div class=\"contents\"><div data-is-streaming=\"false\" class=\"group relative relative pb-3\" style=\"opacity: 1; transform: none;\"><div class=\"font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8\"><div><div class=\"standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown\"><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\"><strong>Client:</strong> CarStyleGarage, Kreuztal / Siegen / Olpe, Germany\n<strong>Stack:</strong> React, responsive layout, multi-step booking form, WhatsApp integration, Google Maps</p>\n<hr class=\"border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5\">\n<h3 class=\"text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold\">The Challenge</h3>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">To create a striking, dark and dynamic website for a premium car wrapping studio. The website had to convey an atmosphere of speed and quality from the very first second, build trust with owners of high-end vehicles, and convert a visitor into a client — without unnecessary phone calls.</p>\n<hr class=\"border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold\"><span data-cms-image=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okcompany/web-studio/main/apps/web/public/uploads/img_1777215148371_1153.png\" data-cms-filename=\"11.png\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"cms-image-token\">[11.png]</span> Hero Section</h4>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">The first thing the visitor sees is a live video of a blue Ford Focus RS driving out of the garage. No static banner — instant immersion into the studio's atmosphere. Yellow accents on a dark background create a distinctive, aggressive brand style. Two buttons lead directly to action: book an appointment online or send a WhatsApp message.</p>\n<hr class=\"border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold\">👉 <code class=\"bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]\">22.png</code> — Services</h4>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">9 services with professional photos of specialists at work — Autoglas Reparatur, Autofolierung, Schaltbare Folien, Lackschutzfolien, Scheibentönung and more. Each card features a real photo and a request button. The client immediately sees what the studio offers and moves straight to booking.</p>\n<hr class=\"border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold\">👉 <code class=\"bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]\">33.png</code> — Online Booking</h4>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">A smart multi-step form in 4 steps. Step one — choosing a service from 6 options with icons. A progress bar at the top shows which step the client is on. No overwhelm — one question at a time. Higher conversion, fewer drop-offs.</p>\n<hr class=\"border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold\">👉 <code class=\"bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]\">44.png</code> — Work Gallery</h4>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">Real projects — Porsche 911 in metallic blue, Mercedes C-Class with paint protection film, Audi A4 with window tinting — filtered by category: Autofolierung, Lackschutz, Scheibentönung, Werbetechnik. The client sees the quality before they even pick up the phone.</p>\n<hr class=\"border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold\">👉 <code class=\"bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]\">55.png</code> — Contact and Map</h4>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">Address, phone, email and opening hours — alongside a live Google Maps embed with a location pin and a 4.8★ rating from 32 reviews shown directly on the map card. Call button and WhatsApp are reachable in a single click.</p>\n<hr class=\"border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold\">👉 <code class=\"bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]\">66.png</code> — Contact Form</h4>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">A clean form with fields for name, email, phone, subject and message. A yellow send button in the brand style. The client can submit a detailed enquiry without opening their email client.</p>\n<hr class=\"border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5\">\n<h3 class=\"text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold\">Visual Style</h3>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">Dark grey and black backgrounds with yellow accents — the studio's brand palette, associated with premium vehicles and professional service. Bold typography, real work photography and a minimalist interface project confidence and expertise.</p>\n<hr class=\"border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5\">\n<h3 class=\"text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold\">The Result</h3>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">The visitor watches a video of a car, browses a gallery of real projects, selects a service in the intuitive form and books an appointment — all without leaving the page. The website works as a showroom and sales manager at the same time: showcase, convince and convert.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"flex justify-start\" role=\"group\" aria-label=\"Message actions\"><div class=\"text-text-300\"><div class=\"text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between\"><div class=\"w-fit\" data-state=\"closed\"><button class=\"inline-flex\n  items-center\n  justify-center\n  relative\n  isolate\n  shrink-0\n  can-focus\n  select-none\n  disabled:pointer-events-none\n  disabled:opacity-50\n  disabled:shadow-non